The accident took place just after 06:00 this morning, between the Bethal and Van Dyksdrift offramps, when the driver of a Hyundai H1 lost control of the vehicle and veered into oncoming traffic.  According to a survivor, the driver of the H1 was headed in eMalahleniâ€™s direction when he swerved into oncoming traffic, striking two cars.  Emergency personnel are currently at the scene, where an investigation is underway, and the lanes heading east have been closed.
